The paper discusses a reinforcement learning algorithm that combines on-policy and off-policy updates to improve efficiency and generalization across diverse environments. This topic is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper, with cs.LG and cs.AI being the most probable.
